# Copy to `.env.production.local` and fill in for LAN distribution builds.
# Use `.env.production.local` (NOT `.env.local`): it is loaded by `vite build`
# (production mode) but NOT by Vitest (test mode), so tests stay keyless/
# deterministic. It is gitignored; the source repo is public so the real key
# must never be committed. For CI installers, set this as the GitHub Actions
# secret VITE_DEFAULT_FAL_API_KEY (wired into the vite build step in
# .github/workflows/build-installers.yml).

# Pre-provisioned default fal.ai engine API key. When set at build time, fresh
# installs default to fal.ai (provider + key) as the active image engine.
# Format: <key_id>:<key_secret>
VITE_DEFAULT_FAL_API_KEY=
